parameters:
"Good morning, everyone. I have an announcement to make, and
it's rather urgent. Some of you may already know, but Suzuki
has been suspended from school."

"The suspension is only for a month, but a suspension is
still a suspension. I hope none of you follow in Suzuki's
footsteps. Remember to behave with moderation."

(My injury wasn't serious, but I still couldn't avoid
suspension.)

(But at least I can relax for a while now, right? Suzuki
won't be coming to school, after all.)

(If Suzuki's suspension starts today and lasts for a
month... I should be able to enjoy a peaceful school life
until Golden Week.)

(Golden Week, huh... Last year, I had so much fun hanging
out with Makoto...)

(That's it! I'll use this Golden Week as an opportunity to
finally confess my feelings to Makoto!)

(I need to prepare everything so I can confess this time.
I'll research the perfect spot for a confession and prepare
a present...)

(Do this... and that... like this... and that kind of
thing...)

And so, as he spent the whole day excitedly planning, the
afternoon classes ended before he knew it. He hurried to
look for Makoto, but she had already left the school.

(Oh no, I got so caught up in planning that I forgot to
apologize to Makoto...)

(But her entourage was always around, making it impossible
to get close. Maybe apologizing at school was never an
option...?)

(It can't be helped. She didn't respond to my message
yesterday, so I'll try to apologize over the phone tonight.
Sigh, I guess I'll head home too...)
"Uh, if X is Z and Y is the dragon and..."
(What kind of problem is he solving?)
